    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第十三位存在，恶之神瑟范斯出现</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗中出现了光，光分裂产生了十二个神圣的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从虚无诞生的十二存在，分享彼此的力量，创造特拉姆，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并与子孙和谐共生。子孙在十二神的庇佑下繁衍兴旺，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，出乎意料地在十二神光芒背后诞生了第十三位存在，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他就是恶之神瑟范斯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/6a1b4ac4493194e2acd46f2e1f6dae71.poster.avif?t=1769053219\" width=624 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/6a1b4ac4493194e2acd46f2e1f6dae71.webm?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/6a1b4ac4493194e2acd46f2e1f6dae71.mp4?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特征</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“UNCHANGED”－动作角色扮演游戏具有可屠杀无数敌人的趣味要素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为快速歼灭大批敌人，获得道具而成长的游戏类型，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《十三月》专注于“横扫战场就会变强”这一个命题开发而成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆脱了典型的构建方式，提供玩家可以自行完成专属游戏内容的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/4f8f890a645e6d367b307649ff127e50.poster.avif?t=1769053219\" width=624 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/4f8f890a645e6d367b307649ff127e50.webm?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/4f8f890a645e6d367b307649ff127e50.mp4?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“UNDEFINED”－自由变换的战斗风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《十三月》里不存在职业。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要选择性别创建角色，玩家就可以根据自己的游戏风格，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更换装备和技能进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然游戏中区分力量、敏捷和智能等，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是没有装配和组合的限制，所以可以拿着剑使用魔法，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者拿着弓箭使用召唤术等，创造专属于自己的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/484a430a927db249969d9854e6a72816.poster.avif?t=1769053219\" width=624 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/484a430a927db249969d9854e6a72816.webm?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/484a430a927db249969d9854e6a72816.mp4?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“UNLIMITED”－无限的技能组合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文分为技能符文和辅助技能符文的链接符文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文可以装配在被称为“符文阵列”的独立空间中使用，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以通过收集或任务奖励获得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文有等级和级别，通过收集可以获取材料，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使符文成长得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“UNSTOPPABLE”－欲罢不能的丰富内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－章节：进行主要情节的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－混沌副本：在主要情节后可进行的游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－首领突袭：最多8人参与的合作内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－荣光圣殿：个人战方式PvP内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－公会：最多可以有50人加入的系统，加入时提供增益等专用福利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/5f121fa0710c49ca646c41065b5b34fe.poster.avif?t=1769053219\" width=624 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/5f121fa0710c49ca646c41065b5b34fe.webm?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549250/extras/5f121fa0710c49ca646c41065b5b34fe.mp4?t=1769053219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
